en.1973DEBD: Tyson Williams has summoned a doctor to the island. He must be feeling under the weather. You have some experience with pain relief, 47. Maybe you can be of assistance?
en.6E920230: Excellent, 47. I hope you can offer the man some assistance...

fr.6E920230: Excellent, 47. J'espère que vous pourrez aider ce pauvre homme…
fr.68B7F322: Faites-vous escorter jusqu'à la chambre de Williams
